org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.federation.store.utils

Class FederationMembershipStateStoreInputValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.federation.store.utils.FederationMembershipStateStoreInputValidator

  • public final class FederationMembershipStateStoreInputValidator
extends Object
    Utility class to validate the inputs to FederationMembershipStateStore, allows a fail fast mechanism for invalid user inputs.
